A cikin ƙasar Bolivia da ke cike da ƙasa, har yanzu ba a manta da yadda aka yi watsi da bakin tekun su ga Chile a cikin rikici mai cike da jini na albarkatu a cikin karni na 19 - yana da sha'awar sake yin tafiya ta hanyar Pacific Ocean.
Wannan fata ta kasance a cikin shekaru da yawa amma yanzu ta kai ga matsayi mafi girma, saboda Bolivia na jiran hukuncin Kotun Shari'a ta Duniya a ranar 1 ga Oktoba, kuma an yi shawarwari a cikin shekaru biyar da suka gabata.
"Bolivia tana da kwanciyar hankali, haɗin kai da kwanciyar hankali a yanzu, kuma tabbas, ƙasar tana fatan kyakkyawan sakamako", in ji Roberto Calzadailla, wani diflomasiyyar Bolivia.
Da yawa daga cikin 'yan Bolivia za su ga hukuncin da aka yanke daga ICJ a kan manyan alloli a duk faɗin ƙasar, suna fatan cewa Kotun Bolivia a Hague za ta yi la'akari da da'awar da ta yi game da shi da jinƙai, bayan shekaru da yawa na tattaunawa, suna ganin Chile ta yi wa Bolivia aiki don yin shawarwari game da ba da damar cikakken iko zuwa teku.
A ranar Litinin, shugaban ƙasar Bolivia mai tasiri Evo Morales - wanda zai fuskanci rikici don sake zaɓe a shekara mai zuwa - yana da kyakkyawan fata ga hukuncin.
"Mun kusan komawa cikin tekun Pacific", in ji shi a watan Agustan da ya gabata.
