Yanzu a shekara ta bakwai, dubban mutane sun yi ta hawan igiyar ruwa zuwa babban ciyawa a Central Park don halartar bikin Global Citizen Festival, ba wai kawai don jin daɗin wasan kwaikwayon Janet Jackson, Cardi B da Shan Mendis ba, har ma don wayar da kan jama'a game da ainihin burin shirin na kawo ƙarshen matsanancin talauci ta 2030.
An kaddamar da bikin Global Citizen a shekarar 2012 kuma an gina shi ne don fadada aikin Global Procurement Project, wata kungiya mai zaman kanta da ke aiki don kawo karshen talauci ta hanyar kara yawan mutanen da ke fama da talauci.
