Wakilan jihohi 10 da kuma District of Columbia sun gabatar da 'Front-of-the-Court Brief' a Washington a ranar Juma'a, suna adawa da sabon manufar kuma suna goyon bayan wani mai neman mafaka.
A watan Agusta, kungiyar 'yancin bil'adama ta Amurka ta shigar da karar ta 'Gres v. Sessions' a kan dokar tarayya, amma ba a bayyana cikakken sunan mai gabatar da karar ba.
