"Federal law ya umurci cewa duk wata da'awar da ake yi game da tsoro za a yanke ta bisa ga takamaiman abubuwan da ake ciki da kuma yanayin da ake yi, amma irin wannan haramcin ya keta wannan ka'idar", in ji Front-of-the-Court Brief.
Masu gabatar da kara sun yi jayayya a kan wannan bayani, inda suka ce dokar hana shigar da 'yan gudun hijira ta lalata tattalin arzikin Amurka, kuma masu neman mafaka sun fi dacewa su zama 'yan kasuwa da kuma samar da "ma'aikata da ake bukata".
