A jawabinsa a taron Majalisar Dinkin Duniya, Ministan Harkokin Wajen kasar, Walid Al Mawlum, ya ce, ana inganta ci gaban da ake samu a kasar.
Ya ce, "Ganin ci gaba da ake samu wajen yaki da ta'addanci, a yau kasar ta fi zama mai dorewa da kwanciyar hankali".
Gwamnati na ci gaba da kokarin dawo da yankunan da 'yan ta'adda suka lalata da su zuwa al'ada
Yanzu da ake da duk abubuwan da ake bukata domin dawowar 'yan gudun hijira, ta'addanci da manufofin tattalin arziki na musamman za su shafi rayuwarsu ta yau da kullum kuma su tilasta musu barin kasar.
Majalisar Dinkin Duniya ta kiyasta cewa kusan mutane miliyan 5.5 ne suka bar kasar tun lokacin da yaki ya barke a shekarar 2011.
Wasu mutane miliyan shida da suka zo ƙasar suna bukatar taimako.
Al-Ma'ullam ya ce gwamnatin Syria za ta amince da duk wani taimako da za a yi don sake gina kasar da ta rushe
Ya jaddada cewa ba za a karɓi taimako na musamman daga ƙasashe da suka yi ƙoƙarin haifar da rikici ba, ko kuma daga wasu.
An sake lashe gasar cin kofin Turai a birnin Paris
Ta doke Amurka ta lashe gasar Ryder Cup ta Turai ta 2018. Ta lashe gasar a Le Golf National da ke birnin Paris, Faransa, ta karshe ta samu ci 10.5 zuwa 16.5.
Wannan shi ne karo na shida da Amurka ta ci nasara a kan ƙasa ta Turai, kuma ba su samu nasarar lashe gasar Ryder Cup ba tun 1993.
A karkashin jagorancin Danish Captain Thomas Jorn, Turai ta sake lashe gasar cin kofin Turai, inda ta ci Amurka da maki 14.5.
A wasan da ya sha wahala a yawancin gasar, dan wasan Amurka Phil Mickelson ya buga shayi a ramin na 16 na Par-3 a cikin ruwa, inda ya ci Francesco Molinari a wasan.
A duk lokacin da ya yi wasan, dan wasan Italiya, Molinari ya yi nasara sosai, kuma ya zama daya daga cikin 'yan wasan hudu da suka ci nasara a gasar, wadda ta fara ne a shekara ta 1979.
